item.title: 【Documentaries】WEB-DL - Taylor Swift - Look What You Made Me Do (Behind the Scenes) - caladan
item.description:
A 15 minutes mini documentary with Behind the Scenes of Look What You Made Me Do. It was part of a Japanese DVD. I extracted the video, cropped the documentary, inverse telecine (ITVC) to get the original progressive 23.976 fps from a 29.97 fps interlaced video (using TFM from Avisynth), resized to proper aspect ratio (Spline36Resize), converted to MP4 AVC (CRF 18) using ffmpeg, muxed A/V with MKV ToolNix.
